{"tid":626314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國妹子排隊想和他打砲　百人斬老外驚傳有愛滋","createTime":"2018-04-12T04:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T13:55:02.000Z","uid":58335,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee6ca8f65b9b816890852dd1e65bf6968609aa6","tid":626314,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"出來混遲早要還！中國一名西班牙、法國混血兒薩米自封自己是《快手》第一外籍網紅「超級老外」，經常在各大社群網站、軟體炫耀妹子主動求愛訊息，用「一日換一女」方式以示自己的高人氣，不料近日卻被爆出有女生跟他愛愛完後感染愛滋病，質問薩米還被反嗆「中國女人就是犯賤」、「活該」，對話訊息流出惹來輿論一片撻伐，雖然薩米已在第一時間出示體檢報告喊冤、質疑遭人陷害，但相關負面八卦包括毆打女友、劈腿、偷拍性愛影片等卻也隨之被一一爆出！<br />\n<br />\n「本人目前單身，渴望找一個善良的中國女人生一個混血寶寶！」皮膚白皙、一頭金髮的薩米憑藉其高大帥氣的外貌在中國享有極高人氣，不僅擁有百萬粉絲還曾登上《湖南衛視》等電視節目，赴中短短4年就名利雙收的他平日除了喜歡炫耀個人的跑車收藏外，沒事還常在網上分享妹子主動找他約砲訊息，「我喜歡又長又大的......。」雖然薩米總是強調他來中國只想找老婆、絕不亂約，沒想到日前卻被傳出他偷吃某網紅後害對方染上愛滋病消息，引發深圳跨文化社交圈人人自危。<br />\n<br />\n「我的體檢報告在這裡！自己看！」薩米為了證明自己的清白，上星期特別跑去醫院做檢查，質疑有人偽造對話訊息想刻意抹黑他，不過多數中國網友看完體檢報告後不但不領情，反批薩米夜路走多遲早會有病，「你不適合在中國！更適合去日本拍A片」、「你這一天一個美女發的，還怪別人說你？」還有網友爆料薩米曾家暴女友鬧上警局，偷拍的性愛影片隨便搜都搜得到，「難道你沒有在淘寶上教人家怎麼搞上女神嗎？你敢說沒有嗎？」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180411/1332612/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332612%2F&d=Dt7%2BsZKySRTPXTrBALTzW%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=67a26e12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180411%2F1332612%2F&h=0cafcb29\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180411/1332612/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_328329bda905d92bebda886db5dffdd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_328329bda905d92bebda886db5dffdd2.jpg&h=e78651b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_f7fbe4442e334fee3bceb9216645b9c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_f7fbe4442e334fee3bceb9216645b9c1.jpg&h=557bd0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_a64037d068d51dd981fd607926a6a222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_a64037d068d51dd981fd607926a6a222.jpg&h=c208ffe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_389b0f0f9bc78eca7f23c43b0e46f380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_389b0f0f9bc78eca7f23c43b0e46f380.jpg&h=6c2e3d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_76abfc1775935881cd2fbe0950512fff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_76abfc1775935881cd2fbe0950512fff.jpg&h=86cfcc35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不料近日卻被爆出有女生跟他愛愛完後感染愛滋病，對話訊息流出惹來輿論一片撻伐。翻攝《微博》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180411/640_d16f79cc50d9e53c324f51f7fa6ff4c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180411%2F640_d16f79cc50d9e53c324f51f7fa6ff4c4.jpg&h=8a614f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然薩米已在第一時間出示體檢報告喊冤、質疑遭人陷害。翻攝《微博》"},{"pid":"867aa63c1ac5b3c3a07fb8d927d5d03810ddb8c5","tid":626314,"uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180412/photo/bkncn-20180412000101012-0412_05011_001_02b.jpg?20180412010758\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180412%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180412000101012-0412_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180412010758&h=40467ed2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0301c844feddab904cf962fb473038ace5111f2b","tid":626314,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo